public class FacetedBundle<K,​F,​T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<FacetedBundle.Entry<F,​T>>
A collection that supports "facets" or markers on individual elements. Provides for efficient retrieval of all elements that have a given subset of facets applied to them.
